PX30 SoCs use a single PHY shared by two display pipelines: MIPI DSI
and LVDS. In the case of the LVDS IP, document the possibility to fill
a PHY handle.

Signed-off-by: Miquel Raynal <miquel.raynal@bootlin.com>
